text: João Diogo Campos Caminata (born 4 January 1995) is a Portuguese professional footballer who plays for CD Cinfães on loan from União da Madeira as a forward. ==Football career== On 17 September 2016, Caminata made his professional debut with União da Madeira in a 2016–17 LigaPro match against Sporting Covilhã. ==References== ==External links== * *Portuguese League profile * Category:1995 births Category:Sportspeople from Funchal Category:Living people Category:Portuguese footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:S.C.U.
